---
// "Real CLIs, your setup": the no-ACP pitch. The braille duck is dux's actual
// welcome-screen art, lifted from src/app/render.rs (ASCII_LOGO_ALT).
const duck = [
  "⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣀⣤⠤⣄⣀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀",
  "⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠔⠉⠀⠀⢸⢰⢸⢰⢰⠉⠢⡀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀",
  "⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⡔⢰⠀⢸⢰⢸⢸⢸⢸⢸⢸⢸⢸⢈⢦⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀",
  "⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣰⢠⢸⠤⣤⠤⢸⢸⢸⢸⢸⠤⠤⢐⢸⢸⡆⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀",
  "⢠⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢹⢸⢸⢸⢸⢸⣤⢰⢲⢤⣄⢸⢸⢸⢸⢸⡇⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀",
  "⠀⠙⡄⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣄⢸⢰⣶⣿⣤⣤⣶⣤⣤⣬⣷⡤⢸⣰⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀",
  "⠀⠀⠈⢦⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠈⢦⢸⢈⠛⠿⣿⣼⣼⠿⠛⠁⢸⡼⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀",
